data-tracking-id="recirc-SEO-tags" class="tags--link link link-txt" href="/food-drink/food/" title="Food">
Food				</a></li></ul></div><h1 class="article-title" itemprop="name">How to Make Pancakes from Scratch</h1><h2 class="article-sub-heading" itemprop="alternativeHeadline"><p>Put away the Bisquick and serve breakfast to the whole family with this ultimate pancake recipe.</p></h2>
